      "content_preview": "Your reservation EHGLP3 for two passengers from PHX to JFK on 2024-05-17 is booked in basic economy cabin. The booking was made on 2024-05-04, and there is no travel insurance on this reservation.\n\nMay I know the reason for cancellation? (change of plan, airline cancelled flight, or other reasons)",
