    },
    {
      "completion_tokens": 94,
      "content_preview": "I understand your concern. However, for this specific reservation, the travel insurance status is recorded as \"no,\" meaning this trip does not have insurance coverage. Refund eligibility is based on the insurance status of the current reservation, not previous trips.\n\nGiven that, the cancellation for change of plan in…",
